[Amit Varma]: So that sounds fascinating.

02:36:12.020 --> 02:36:15.740
[Amit Varma]: So, you know, one of the things that I enjoy about your newsletter, of course, is all the

02:36:15.740 --> 02:36:20.860
[Amit Varma]: references to Bollywood, which are quite wonderful, like you have this fabulous quote, you have

